            "pub_date": "2026-04-13 16:56:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "在岸人民幣兌美元收跌5點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在岸人民幣兌美元官方收6.8338，較上日官方收盤價跌5點，較上日夜盤收盤跌33點。</p>\n</div>",
